52 ** http: www.nxp.com
53 ** mail: support@nxp.com
54 **
55 ** Revisions:
56 ** - rev. 1.0 (2014-03-27)
57 ** Initial version.
58 ** - rev. 1.1 (2014-05-26)
59 ** I2S registers TCR2/RCR2 and others were changed.
60 ** FLEXIO register FLEXIO_VERID has now bitfields: FEATURE, MINOR, MAJOR.
61 ** Names of the bitfields of the FLEXIO_SHIFTBUF have been changed to the appropriate register name e.g.: FLEXIO_SHIFTBUFBBS_SHIFTBUFBBS.
62 ** Peripheral_BASES macros has been changed to Peripheral_BASE_PTRS, e.g.: ADC_BASES to ADC_BASE_PTRS.
63 ** Clock configuration for high range external oscillator has been added.
64 ** RFSYS module access has been added.
65 ** - rev. 1.2 (2014-07-10)
66 ** GPIO - Renamed modules PTA,PTB,PTC,PTD,PTE to GPIOA,GPIOB,GPIOC,GPIOD,GPIOE.
67 ** UART0 - UART0 module renamed to UART2.
68 ** I2S - removed MDR register.
69 ** - rev. 1.3 (2014-08-21)
70 ** UART2 - Removed ED register.
71 ** UART2 - Removed MODEM register.
72 ** UART2 - Removed IR register.
73 ** UART2 - Removed PFIFO register.
74 ** UART2 - Removed CFIFO register.
75 ** UART2 - Removed SFIFO register.
76 ** UART2 - Removed TWFIFO register.
77 ** UART2 - Removed TCFIFO register.
78 ** UART2 - Removed RWFIFO register.
79 ** UART2 - Removed RCFIFO register.
80 ** USB - Removed bitfield REG_EN in CLK_RECOVER_IRC_EN register.
81 ** SIM - Changed bitfield value MCGIRCLK to LIRC_CLK of bitfield CLKOUTSEL in SOPT2 register.
82 ** SIM - Removed bitfield DIEID in SDID register.
83 ** - rev. 1.4 (2014-09-01)
84 ** USB - USB0_CTL0 was renamed to USB0_OTGCTL register.
85 ** USB - USB0_CTL1 was renamed to USB0_CTL register.
86 ** - rev. 1.5 (2014-09-05)
87 ** USB - Renamed USBEN bitfield of USB0_CTL was renamed to USBENSOFEN.
88 ** - rev. 1.6 (2015-07-29)
89 ** Correction of backward compatibility.
90 ** - rev. 1.7 (2016-02-02)
91 ** FGPIO - Add FGPIO registers.
92 ** - rev. 1.8 (2016-06-24)
93 ** USB - OTGCTL register was removed.
94 ** USB - Bit RESUME was added in CTL register.
95 **
96 ** ###################################################################
97 */

848 /* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
849  -- DMA Peripheral Access Layer
850  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
851 
858 typedef struct {
859  uint8_t RESERVED_0[256];
860  struct { /* offset: 0x100, array step: 0x10 */
861  __IO uint32_t SAR;
862  __IO uint32_t DAR;
863  union { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
864  __IO uint32_t DSR_BCR;
865  struct { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
866  uint8_t RESERVED_0[3];
867  uint8_t DSR;
868  } DMA_DSR_ACCESS8BIT;
869  };
870  __IO uint32_t DCR;
871  } DMA[4];
872 } DMA_Type;
